<br>
I was 57 with 200 wis and minor mana gear.  Used Form of the Howler and went oom when the othmirs had less than 150 HP left.  Needed to med kite for that final nuke.  (Lightning Strike was enough to finish them off)<br>
<br>
I am 58 now with all the same gear I had in 57.  I use Fist of Karana and Spirit of Eagle now, and I have half a bub of mana left after the quad.<br>
